    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. While it still runs, the engine has a noticeable knock, the transmission shifts roughly, and there are several fluid leaks that need immediate repair. The exterior has substantial body damage, including rusted panels and peeling clear coat, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is best suited for a mechanic looking for a project or for use as a parts vehicle.",
