      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction, preserved in pristine showroom condition. This specimen exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a history of fastidious maintenance and uncompromising care. Every mechanical system operates with the precision of its original manufacture, while the aesthetic presentation remains flawless. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that represents the absolute zenith of its class.",
      "price": 44900.0,
